\id 2JN - Jacalteco (Eastern) -Guatemala 1997 (DBL -2013)
\h 2 JUAN
\toc1 Iscab Carta Naj San Juan
\toc2 2 Juan
\toc3 2Jn
\mt1 ISCAB CARTA NAJ SAN JUAN
\c 1
\s1 Cuybanile yin̈ isyelal coxahann̈en coba
\p 
\v 1 Hanin icham winaj\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Yin̈ castilla haꞌ chalilo \fk anciano.\f* intiꞌan, chintzꞌibn̈etojan huneꞌ carta tiꞌ tawet wanab, hach saybilxa yu Comam Dios, yeb tetej hawuninal. Yin̈ caw yeli caw xahan ayex wuhan, yaj maẍn̈etajinan to haꞌ hunpaxo ebnaj juẍtaj, yeb ebix janab caw xaohtan̈en cuybanile caw yeli.
\v 2 Caw xahan ayex wuhan, yu huneꞌ caw isyelal ayco yin̈ janma. Aycꞌo cocꞌatan̈ huneꞌ isyelal tiꞌ sunilbal tiempo.
\v 3 Haꞌojab Comam Dios yeb Comam Jesucristo, Iscꞌahol Comam Dios chianayo iscꞌulchꞌanil iscꞌul teyiban̈, cat istzꞌay iscꞌul teyin̈, cat yakꞌnipaxo akꞌancꞌulal teyet yin̈ isyelal, cat quexisxahann̈en Comam.
\p 
\v 4 Caw tzalacan̈ incꞌulan yet wilnihan haywan̈ hawunin caw yijem yin̈ cuybanile caw yel chala, hacaꞌ yute yakꞌnicano Comam Dios jet.
\v 5 Wal tinan̈ xin, caw chiwalan teyet tato caw yilal xahan chijil coba hununon̈. Huneꞌ chejbanile chiwakꞌan teyet tiꞌ, caw mach babelto heyabeni, caw hataxticꞌa yet joc yul iskꞌab Comam Dios, hatax tuꞌ yichi jabeni.
\v 6 Tato chicoyije chejbanile chal Comam Dios, chaliloj ta caw chijoche tzet chal Comam. Huneꞌ chejbanile xajabe yettax joc yul iskꞌab Comam Dios, haꞌ ton coxahann̈en coba hununon̈.
\s1 Ebnaj chiakꞌni subchaho anma
\p 
\v 7 Wal tinan̈ xin, caw txꞌiꞌalxa ebnaj lekꞌtiꞌwom chiecꞌ yul sat yiban̈kꞌinal tiꞌ. Chilan xin yalni ebnaj ta mach hulicꞌo Comam Jesucristo yin̈ anmahil yin̈ caw isyelal. Haꞌ huntekꞌan ebnaj tuꞌ chiakꞌni subchaho anma. Caw xin ayco ishowal ebnaj yin̈ Comam.
\v 8 Caw nann̈e heyu xin, tajca caw nabn̈e cheyu yin̈ hemunil yin̈ yet Comam. Wal xin caw tzꞌajanojab chu hechahni ispaj selel hemunil tet Comam Dios.
\p 
\v 9 Macn̈eticꞌa chipalcꞌoncan̈ yiban̈ cuybanile aycano jet yu Comam Jesucristo cat isbejnicanoj, chalilo chal tuꞌ ta machi Comam Dios yul yanma. Wal taca tzujan yinta cuybanile akꞌbilcano yu Comam xin, wal tuꞌ caw ayayto Comam Dios yeb Iscꞌahol Comam yul yanma.
\v 10 Tato ay hunu mac chiapni tecꞌatan̈, nan xin cuybanile ikꞌbil yu, mach chechah yul heyatut, yeb xin mach chekꞌambe hanicꞌ ye iscꞌul.
\v 11 Tato chexoc hekꞌambeꞌ hanicꞌ ye iscꞌul, chalilo chal tuꞌ ta haꞌ hunex yin̈ huneꞌ istxꞌojal chiswatxꞌe tuꞌ.
\s1 Islahobal carta
\p 
\v 12 Caw hantan̈e tzet chiwochehan chiwaltojan teyet, yaj mach chiwochehan chintzꞌibn̈etojan yin̈ hum tiꞌ, yuto toxan̈e chiwechmahan intohan quexintuclenojan cat xin cotzoteli, hac tuꞌ caw chitzꞌajna tzalahilal yul janma.
\p 
\v 13 Haꞌ ej yuninal hanoh ay bey tiꞌ, sicꞌbililo yu Comam Dios, chikꞌambeni hanicꞌ hawe bey tuꞌ. ¡Hacojab tuꞌ!
